title: Tech hits the road for matches vs. USCB, SMU - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech hits the road for matches vs. USCB, SMU - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, TEXAS – The Texas Tech women's tennis team hits the road this weekend for a two-match trip on Friday and Sunday.The No. 34 ranked Lady Raiders (6-3) will begin the weekend with UC Santa Barbara (6-5) at 5 p.m. on Friday at TCU's Bayard H. Friedman Tennis Center.
